2BR / 1Ba 850ft2 available nov 1 apartment w/d in unit no smoking attached garage/ 2br - 850ft2 -Description
->Very Bright and Spacious single-level 2 bedroom, 850 sq.ft. townhouse located in the trendy Avondale community at Yonge & Sheppard;
-> Viewings start in early October - Don't miss out! Applications available immediately (reference and credit checks required).

Unit Features:
>> Large master bedroom (approx 22' x 12') with walkout to balcony;
>> Newly renovated bathroom (Oct'20) and professionally painted;
>> 2nd Bedroom/Office space;
>> Kitchen with stainless steel appliances and separate eating area;
>> Living room with gas fireplace;
>> Underground parking spot;
>> No elevators to wait for (reducing COVID risk) and no stairs within unit for improved accessibility.

Available: November 1st, 2020

Ready to Move In!
>> All utilities included;
>> California shutters on all bedroom windows;
>>Walking distance to Starbucks, TTC, whole Foods, Salon, Rabba, restaurants, movie theater and parks. Easy access to 401 and 2 subway lines.
>>Great Value - save over $400/month for similar space compared to Harrison Garden rentals.

2BR / 0Ba cats are OK - purrr dogs are OK - wooof furnished apartment/ 2br -Located in trendy Leslieville at 240 Highfield Road (Greenwood & Gerrard), on a quiet tree-lined residential street just steps to all Amenities & Convenient Transportation (i.e. closest subway station is Greenwood and just steps to the Gerrard 24/7 Streetcar and Queen line). Close to Ryerson and George Brown Campus.
This bright & renovated never lived in before 2nd floor 2 bedroom unit is available immediately!
$1195 + hydro

FEATURES:
- Air Conditioning;
- Large Private Deck (perfect for BBQ to enjoy & kick-back);
- On-Site Laundry;
- Modern washroom;
- Spacious bedroom;
- Modern Floor;
- Fireplace;
- Parking available!

LOCATION: Convenient & Trendy Location
Enjoy the best of both worlds with beautiful active parks and tree-lined streets, as well as trendy restaurants, brunch spots, lounges, shops and cafes in your own neighbourhood. Also just moments from all amenities, including: Grocery Stores (No Frills), Drug Store, Video Store, Gym (Goodlife), Mall and countless other shops. This unit is also just a short drive to The Beaches, Little India, China Town East and Greektown/The Danforth.
Easy Transportation --
This is a perfect location to commute from! Walk to the 24/7 Gerrard Streetcar Line (be downtown in just 15-20 minutes!), Greenwood subway line. And just a quick walk to the Queen Streetcar line. Also just a quick drive to either Don Valley Parkway or the Gardiner Expressway. Perfect for George Brown, UofT and Ryerson staff/students or a couple.

